      • RDFPath

        public RDFPath(java.lang.String... path)
        Constructs a new RDFPath from the specified chain of property/class URIs. Each string can also be a property/class URI pair in the format "propertyURI some classURI". If the path consists of a single string, that string will be split on commas before being processed.
        Parameters:
        path - the chain of property/class URIs
